metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Mario Circuit 3 - Mario Kart Wii has complexity on par with the typical song, having near-average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity and Chord-Melody Tension and below-average scores in Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
